      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  diagnosed peripheral post-operative neuropathic pain

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  hypersensitivity to capsaicin

          -  pregnancy

          -  diabetes mellitus

          -  treatment of face
